  "segments": [
    {
      "segment_id": "58cfcc64",
      "source_content": "---\ntitle: Simulate Host Faults\n---",
      "source_content_hash": "94707a03d4541d6f3e6522d35974a35355113fcac9ac4269ae2ec4d449895c04",
      "node_type": "yaml",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_58cfcc64"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "e7ec8f99",
      "source_content": "This document introduces how to simulate host shutdown faults using Chaosd.",
      "source_content_hash": "6cc42c71ebff76d8c62f7583fdb3f588787f5378df037ca2e37e734da98a0819",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "このドキュメントでは、Chaosdを使用してホストシャットダウンの障害をシミュレートする方法について説明します。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "a703643c",
      "source_content": "## View the help information of host shutdown experiments",
      "source_content_hash": "f20b52871bb6b232d3589387369d0f2b36ab01b7cab7b645addb615c08ebfebe",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "## ホストシャットダウン実験のヘルプ情報を表示"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "53eaf0e1",
      "source_content": "Before creating a fault experiment, you can run the following command to view the help information of host shutdown experiments:",
      "source_content_hash": "5de405d39ccadb6a243e2af9d511aaea5be6a0b8558ad9c080f825e1e320d788",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "障害実験を作成する前に、以下のコマンドを実行してホストシャットダウン実験のヘルプ情報を確認できます："
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "43a8bc7e",
      "source_content": "```bash\nchaosd attack host shutdown -h\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "4e6db373c1f0c6eff2a82e1264e23cb0d60dcc54b1605e10b89ef9e21ca07f0b",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_43a8bc7e"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "cf898102",
      "source_content": "The output is as follows:",
      "source_content_hash": "e393a74ababf246af54d3aaa19b45a8f23cc8470c3659248fb33a6888578f447",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "出力は以下のようになります："
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "93be3c14",
      "source_content": "```bash\nshutdowns system, this action will trigger shutdown of the host machine\n\nUsage:\n  chaosd attack host shutdown [flags]\n\nFlags:\n  -h, --help   help for shutdown\n\nGlobal Flags:\n      --log-level string   the log level of chaosd, the value can be 'debug', 'info', 'warn' and 'error'\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "a3ea6c5e601715b8c23c98ab0053e0fd00d8ba2f30ab4f5c7c31dcddec668b39",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_93be3c14"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "d06306f7",
      "source_content": "## Create a host shutdown experiment",
      "source_content_hash": "9d9ba94b7b251a3d75ba18d726a83f773d0e1e6eb4560aa51355d7382b756180",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "## ホストシャットダウン実験の作成"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "73ab96a3",
      "source_content": "To create a host shutdown experiment, run the following command:",
      "source_content_hash": "eac59f35f8cc6f51d00e65aae2a5a8d1d939df59608827e3b528fb239c1b0682",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "ホストシャットダウン実験を作成するには、以下のコマンドを実行します："
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "6543a19e",
      "source_content": "```bash\nchaosd attack host shutdown\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "938d815170ed4cd88afa7b2e14e8d744dff90fe180473fe2b2da9289da9eb98d",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_6543a19e"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "135468ee",
      "source_content": "The example output is as follows:",
      "source_content_hash": "f76c341c1e48dfe3c1855db286fbb0a7173ee15fb762305a859d263d10ac5814",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "出力例は以下のようになります："
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "a11df754",
      "source_content": "```bash\nchaosd attack host shutdown\nShutdown successfully, uid: 4bc9b74a-5fe2-4038-b4f3-09ae95b57694\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "e33d59f8650d9bb9503abcef14192c5aaecc91b1cbe0c415c7fde193cf04e1f2",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_a11df754"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "aa1e7006",
      "source_content": "After executing this command, your host will shut down after all processes are closed.",
      "source_content_hash": "7158d632728c4c149d9523c5f7a72375c6a8cbe23f93622d6b7cdb084a965bd8",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "このコマンドを実行すると、すべてのプロセスが終了した後にホストがシャットダウンします。"
      }
    }
  ],
